translate portuguese jamiestudy0_7d7e4c95:

    # "I knock on the door and a few seconds later Jamie rushes to the door and answers."
    "Bato à porta e, alguns segundos depois, a Jamie corre para a porta e abre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:13
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_5bae9e51:

    # gnd "Hey, [pcname]. What's up?"
    gnd "Olá, [pcname]. Como estás?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:14
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_49bf17fe:

    # pc "Not much, just thought I'd see what you're up to and if you wanted to hang out."
    pc "Nada de especial, só pensei em ver o que estavas a fazer e se querias sair um bocado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:15
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_21baa282:

    # gnd "Oh, well I was about to start studying for a test."
    gnd "Ah, bem, estava prestes a começar a estudar para um teste."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:16
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_6cc3a5ff:

    # pc "Ah, well I'll leave you alone then. I should probably get some studying in too."
    pc "Ah, bem, então vou deixar-te em paz. Provavelmente também devia estudar um pouco."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:17
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_15ee3cd5:

    # gnd "Want to join me? We could study together."
    gnd "Queres juntar-te a mim? Podíamos estudar juntos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:22
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:23
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_e5466e94:

    # gnd "Great!"
    gnd "Ótimo!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:25
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_b1fa7b3c:

    # gnd "Come on now, don't be pervy. Do you want to study or not?"
    gnd "Vá lá, não sejas pervertido. Queres estudar ou não?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:30
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:31
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_e5466e94_1:

    # gnd "Great!"
    gnd "Ótimo!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:34
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_77d566bd:

    # gnd "Okay then. Well I'll see you later then."
    gnd "Está bem, então. Bem, vejo-te mais tarde."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:35
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:36
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_1557defd:

    # "With that, she goes back inside and I walk back over to my house."
    "Com isso, ela volta para dentro e eu caminho de volta para minha casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:41
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_77d566bd_1:

    # gnd "Okay then. Well I'll see you later then."
    gnd "Está bem, então. Bem, até logo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:42
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_209b1712_1:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:43
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_1557defd_1:

    # "With that, she goes back inside and I walk back over to my house."
    "Dito isto, ela volta para dentro e eu volto para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:49
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_a0d94bd3:

    # pc "I'll just grab my laptop real quick."
    pc "Vou só buscar o meu portátil rapidinho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:50
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_0d7dfb6d:

    # gnd "Alrighty."
    gnd "Tudo bem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:53
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_d47d13e8:

    # "I rush home and run up the stairs, grabbing my laptop from the desk in my bedroom, then run back down and over to Jamie's house again."
    "Corro para casa e subo as escadas a correr, pego no meu portátil da secretária do meu quarto, depois desço a correr e volto para a casa da Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:56
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_17909979:

    # "She is waiting right by the door for me."
    "Ela está à minha espera mesmo à porta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:57
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_e90b21a6:

    # gnd "Let's go up to my bedroom."
    gnd "Vamos subir para o meu quarto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:58
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_050f909c:

    # pc "Sounds good."
    pc "Parece-me bem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:61
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_2d11a3f1:

    # "I follow her up the stairs to her bedroom and we both sit on the bed."
    "Sigo-a pelas escadas até ao quarto dela e sentamo-nos os dois na cama."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:62
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_cecfb5d5:

    # "She pulls out some books that she had to read while I open up the essay that I have been working on."
    "Ela tira alguns livros que tinha de ler, enquanto eu abro o ensaio em que tenho estado a trabalhar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:63
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_43cd5788:

    # "We don't talk a whole lot, but occasionally I see her looking up at me smiling."
    "Não falamos muito, mas, de vez em quando, vejo-a a olhar para mim a sorrir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:65
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_0507e3ef:

    # "Which subject should I study?"
    "Que matéria devo estudar?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:71
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_562e0a86:

    # "I try to focus on my work, but it is difficult with her lying there like that."
    "Tento concentrar-me no meu trabalho, mas é difícil com ela ali deitada assim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:72
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_6306f9ee:

    # "Part of me just wants to toss my laptop aside and roll over on top of her."
    "Parte de mim só quer atirar o portátil para o lado e deitar-me em cima dela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:73
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_30a96a1d:

    # "I wonder what she would do. Would she say no? Would she be into it?"
    "Pergunto-me o que ela faria. Diria que não? Gostaria da ideia?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:74
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_6ab7d82e:

    # "I decide not to push my luck for now. Not until she gives me a clear signal."
    "Decido não abusar da sorte por agora. Não até ela me dar um sinal claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:75
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_388afa61:

    # "Our relationship is still a little rocky after the way I had treated her when we were younger."
    "A nossa relação ainda está um pouco instável depois da forma como a tratei quando éramos mais novos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:76
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_b3f8928f:

    # "I like the way that things are going and I don't want to ruin them."
    "Gosto da forma como as coisas estão a correr e não quero estragá-las."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:77
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_08d0a0f6:

    # "She will make it clear to me when she is ready."
    "Ela vai deixar-me claro quando estiver pronta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:78
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_cd9b1b6c:

    # "After a couple of hours of working on the essay, I feels like it is pretty much done."
    "Depois de algumas horas a trabalhar no ensaio, sinto que está praticamente pronto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:79
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_f7da6361:

    # "Which is good, because right then I hear the door downstairs open."
    "O que é bom, porque, nesse preciso momento, ouço a porta lá em baixo a abrir-se."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:83
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_052a.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_052a.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:84
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_694762e8:

    # gnd "Oh shit, what time is it?"
    gnd "Merda, que horas são?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:86
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_052b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_052b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:87
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_90448217:

    # gnd "I didn't realize that it was so late. Daddy will kill you if he finds you in my bedroom."
    gnd "Não me apercebi que era tão tarde. O pai mata-te se te encontrar no meu quarto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:88
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_4bba0230:

    # pc "Should I hide?"
    pc "Devo esconder-me?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:90
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_02419fb6:

    # gnd "I'll distract him and get him into the back yard. When we're back there, you sneak out the front."
    gnd "Vou distraí-lo e levá-lo para o quintal. Quando estivermos lá atrás, sai pela frente."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:91
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_238bde54:

    # pc "Got it."
    pc "Entendi."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:92
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_0784ddae:

    # gnd "I had a good time studying with you tonight, by the way."
    gnd "A propósito, gostei muito de estudar contigo esta noite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:93
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_b7756d1b:

    # gnd "We should do it again sometime."
    gnd "Devíamos repetir isto um dia destes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:94
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_2951ed74:

    # pc "Definitely."
    pc "Sem dúvida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:96
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_fd213b46:

    # gnd "Okay, stay here until you hear us go out into the back yard."
    gnd "Ok, fica aqui até nos ouvires a sair para o quintal."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:97
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Ok."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:100
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_18efe5b1:

    # "With that, she walks out of the bedroom and down the stairs. I tuck my laptop under my arm and wait."
    "Dito isto, ela sai do quarto e desce as escadas. Coloco o meu portátil debaixo do braço e espero."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:101
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_23a9e57a:

    # "After a few moments, I hear the back door open and shut and I take the opportunity to sneak out and down the stairs."
    "Passados alguns instantes, ouço a porta das traseiras a abrir e a fechar e aproveito a oportunidade para sair sorrateiramente e descer as escadas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:104
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_d7055002:

    # "I can hear them talking in the back of the house as I sneak out the front door and creep back over to my house."
    "Consigo ouvi-los a conversar nas traseiras da casa enquanto saio pela porta da frente e volto sorrateiramente para a minha casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:106
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_0859cfec:

    # "That was close. I mean, he wouldn't have really killed me though, right?"
    "Foi por pouco. Quer dizer, ele não me teria matado a sério, pois não?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieStudy/jamiestudy0.rpy:107
translate portuguese jamiestudy0_9979a58c:

    # "Right?"
    "Certo?"

